Sentencas: Despite some the advantages of the solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC), one of the greatest challenges that hinders the SOFC from rising to dominance in the field of power generation is its high fabrication cost.
Titulo: Aqueous tape casting technique for the fabrication of Sc0.1Ce0.01Zr0.89O2+Δ ceramic for electrolyte-supported solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: As a solution, the tape casting process has been widely used to fabricate low-cost, uniform and thin SOFC electrolytes.
Titulo: Aqueous tape casting technique for the fabrication of Sc0.1Ce0.01Zr0.89O2+Δ ceramic for electrolyte-supported solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Compared to organic-based tape casting, aqueous-based tape casting is a much more environmentally friendly technique.
Titulo: Aqueous tape casting technique for the fabrication of Sc0.1Ce0.01Zr0.89O2+Δ ceramic for electrolyte-supported solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: In this work, a large-area electrolyte-supported solid oxide fuel cell was fabricated by this technique together with sintering.
Titulo: Aqueous tape casting technique for the fabrication of Sc0.1Ce0.01Zr0.89O2+Δ ceramic for electrolyte-supported solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: A 10 cm x 10 cm and 0.17 mm thick supported Sc0.1Ce0.01Zr0-89O2+Delta, (SSZ) electrolyte was obtained with good flatness, low ohmic resistance and high open-circuit voltage.
Titulo: Aqueous tape casting technique for the fabrication of Sc0.1Ce0.01Zr0.89O2+Δ ceramic for electrolyte-supported solid oxide fuel cell
